February 3rd 2015

UIComposer sannity test steps for February release:

1.  Login to Norman (sign up if have not done)
2.  Click on Projects menu from left size
3.  Create a project, for example name 'MyProject1'
4.  Click on project MyProject1
5.  Click on first default page (page1)
6.  Drag and drop a Button control from the OpenUI5 control list on the right side.  Verify drag and drop is working.
7.  Click plus button (+) on to add a new page, verify new page displayed
8.  Click on setting gear icon next to Library, select 'Angular' option  (this is to check UICatalog service working)
9.  Drag and drop ProgressBar in new page, verify ProgressBar displayed in new page (page3)
10. Click Projects menu from left size
11. Verify Projects page displayed  1 projects, 3 pages, 0 assets (this is to check projects service working)
12. Verify project name (MyProject1) displayed correctly
13. Click on MyProject1, verify three pages displayed, page1 selected
14. Click camera icon from top blue bar to save a snapshot
15.  Verify message displayed saying snapshot is save successfully.
